Package: libgsni1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: StatusNotifierItem D-Bus tray icon library (runtime)
 libgsni implements the StatusNotifierItem (SNI) D-Bus protocol
 for GTK4 applications, providing system tray icons with menus,
 tooltips and scroll events.

